    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation without the premium price of a newer-looking car. While the engine and transmission are in good working order and have been serviced regularly, the exterior shows visible signs of use, including several noticeable scratches, faded paint on the hood, and a few small dings. The interior is clean but exhibits some wear on the upholstery and floor mats. It is a dependable driver that performs well on the road, making it a practical option for daily commuting or as a secondary utility vehicle.",
