    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 inline-six engine. This high-compression power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver exceptional throttle response and a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. Chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from proactively reinforced rear subframe mounting points and refreshed bushings. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement. While the finish shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the powertrain integrity and torsional rigidity remain excellent. This is a performance-first example optimized for technical driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
