      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains its deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest signs of a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is free of rips or stains, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. It starts eagerly, idles smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it\u2019s ready for its next owner. If you are looking for a reliable, well-cared-for example that hasn't been neglected, this is the one.",
